lead_paragraph: Chris Iannetta hit a two-run homer in his spring training debut for the Seattle Mariners, who opened their exhibition schedule with a 7-0 win Wednesday over the San Diego Padres.

headline.print_headline: Iannetta Homers, Drives in 3 as Mariners Beat Padres 7-0
